{"tid":1344180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［推撚到陽萎聰回應］新城市廣場同南邊圍村同樣都係私人地方 點解一個入得點解一個就門口企","createTime":"2019-07-21T20:52:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T01:06:27.000Z","uid":274341,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d492f66cea91a31f920bb890fca4ab28ed7575b5","tid":1344180,"uid":274341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T20:52:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Vd5y0S0i3Zo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVd5y0S0i3Zo&d=D9%2BIkncl4BF5lZ8wPV9kyAZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=a17760dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Vd5y0S0i3Zo</a><br />\n鏗鏘有力 擲地有聲<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有干犯違法行為嘅人走左入商場 係咪有責任跟埋入去呢？？？</span></span><br />\n言下之意 即係私唔咩私人地對你地黎講<br />\n都係可以有條件咁去無視<br />\n同樣地 南邊圍前面啲地係私人地 （照返今日直播 啲黑警係咁同啲傳媒講話係私人地方 唔可以再向前）<br />\n佢地就企定定成晚幫人守門口 <br />\n仲俾人影住啲防暴同啲白衫鄉黑係到吹水<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「喂盧偉聰你含撚啦 屌你老母扮傻」</span>"},{"pid":"058a52d208ca9cc09490aadd277dca19371c0bd2","tid":1344180,"uid":274341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T20:55:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">當然更加要留意 上環開左36槍 仲有手足俾人爆頭</span></span>"},{"pid":"f71a54bc230dd5e56ad0bff89e60c4e4a33025ee","tid":1344180,"uid":242737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T21:02:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee319c395941d88551fd84c9a9e58b18feb6f365","tid":1344180,"uid":5303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T21:06:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e8%a6%81%e8%81%9e/article/20190717/s00001/1563301379081/6%e5%95%86%e5%a0%b4%e5%9c%b0%e5%a5%91%e5%87%86%e8%ad%a6%e5%9f%b7%e6%b3%95-%e5%8c%85%e6%8b%ac%e5%a4%aa%e5%8f%a4%e6%96%b0%e5%9f%8e%e5%b8%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e8%25a6%2581%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190717%2Fs00001%2F1563301379081%2F6%25e5%2595%2586%